Day 2 — March 2 — Core Services Layer: @critical
  Goal: CryptoService, WalletService, repositories, queues, validation all working.
  T2.1 CryptoService (Envelope Encryption): @critical
    ☐ Implement MEK derivation: PBKDF2 600K iterations + SHA-512 + per-wallet salt
    ☐ Implement encrypt: plaintext → random DEK → AES-256-GCM → wrapped output
    ☐ Implement decrypt: wrapped → derive MEK → unwrap DEK → AES-256-GCM → plaintext
    ☐ Implement memory safety: .fill(0) in finally blocks for all key buffers
    ☐ Verify invariants 1-4 compliance
    ☐ Write 5+ unit tests: roundtrip, wrong key, tampered data, different salts, memory zeroing
  T2.2 WalletService: @critical
    ☐ Implement generateWallet() — Keypair.generate() + encrypt + store
